Four people, including two children, were killed when a Ford Figo hatchback sedan struck an articulated truck on the N4 near Machadodorp last night. The Mpumalanga Department of Community Safety confirmed that a man and woman was also killed in the crash. The bodies of the deceased were trapped inside the wreck and jaws of life had to be used to extract the bodies. The accident occurred around 19:00. The identities of the deceased have not been released. The cause of the accident is under investigation.